    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "The sacrifices and the festival. After fire from heaven had devoured the sacrifices, and Solomon had praised the Lord for the fulfilment of His word, and sought for the congregation the further bestowal of the divine blessing (",
        "children": []
