        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Kings 8:54-61",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "), the dedication of the temple was concluded by a great thank-offering, of which we have in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2 Chronicles 7:5",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", ",
        "children": []
      },
